<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Messenger Bot</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 0 20px; color: #333; }
    h1 { color: #0084ff; }
    code { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; }
    .status { display: inline-block; background: #e6f4ea; color: #1e8e3e; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Messenger Bot</h1>
  <p><span class="status">&#x2705; Webhook is live</span></p>
  <p>Your bot is running. To connect it to Facebook Messenger:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Set up your <a href="https://developers.facebook.com/apps" target="_blank">Facebook App</a> and subscribe to a Page.</li>
    <li>Set <code>VERIFY_TOKEN</code>, <code>PAGE_ACCESS_TOKEN</code>, and <code>APP_SECRET</code> in your <code>.env</code> file.</li>
    <li>Point your webhook to <code>/webhook</code> on this server.</li>
    <li>Visit <code>/profile?mode=all&amp;verify_token=YOUR_TOKEN</code> to configure the Messenger Profile.</li>
  </ol>
</body>
</html>
